title: U.S. women who have given oral sex to a male in their lifetime , by age group
summary: This bar chart has 10 columns on the x axis representing Age group, and Share of respondents in each Age group on the y axis.
The Share of respondents is highest at Age group 25-29 and lowest at Age group 14-15.
The highest Age group 25-29 has 76.0 more Share of respondents than the lowest Age group 14-15.
